data.description: One or more photo(s) has been virtually staged. Discover the epitome of modern living in this exquisite two-story home constructed with a solid concrete block foundation. As you step inside, you'll be greeted by a spacious and open-concept floor plan on the ground level. This inviting space seamlessly integrates a well-appointed kitchen, a generous living area, and an elegant dining space, creating the perfect environment for entertaining and relaxation. Step through the sliding glass doors, and you'll find an outdoor patio, an ideal spot for alfresco dining or simply enjoying the Florida sunshine—venture upstairs to explore the upper level, where luxury and comfort abound. The oversized owner's suite offers ample room for a king-size bed, boasts a substantial walk-in closet, and features an ensuite bathroom complete with a double vanity, adding a touch of opulence to your daily routine. Three additional bedrooms share a well-appointed second bathroom, making this home perfect for family living. Additionally, the loft on the upper level provides a versatile space that can be customized to your needs, whether it's a home office, playroom, or cozy retreat. This home has all the essential appliances, including a refrigerator, built-in dishwasher, electric range, and microwave, ensuring your culinary endeavors are a breeze. Take advantage of the opportunity to make this your new home!
